<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="change-v">change <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /tʃeɪndʒ/    美 /tʃeɪndʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>变化；改变：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The two things that <strong>change</strong> your <strong>life</strong> are the people you meet and books you read.
有两种东西可以改变你的生活：你遇到的人和你读的书。</p><footer>2016 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The neighborhood which I used to live in has changed a lot.
我曾住过的那个居民区变化很大。</p><footer>2009 全国</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>change (from sth) to / into sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The driver of the car didn’t see his traffic light had changed from orange to red.
小车司机没看到交通信号灯由黄变红了。</p><footer>2010 全国改</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>change sb / sth into / to sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With a wave of her magic stick, she changed the prince into a frog.
她魔杖一挥，把王子变成了一只青蛙。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>更换；替换；(给…) 换 (衣服)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The time of the meeting has been <strong>changed from</strong> 10 a.m. <strong>to</strong> 9 a.m. 
开会时间由上午10点改到了9点。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>change a tyre / the sheets / jobs
换轮胎/床单/工作</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The three boys were fed, bathed and <strong>changed into</strong> their nightclothes.
给3个男孩子喂了饭，洗了澡，再给他们换上睡衣。</p><footer>2011 江西</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sarah, hurry up. I'm afraid you won't have time to <strong>get changed</strong> before the party.
萨拉，快点！恐怕聚会开始前你没有时间换衣服了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>交换；互换：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>change sth with sb:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Can I change seats with you?
我能跟你换座位吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She may be rich, but I wouldn’t want to change places with her.
她也许很有钱，但是我也不愿意和她交换位置。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>把 (钱) 换成 (零钱)；兑换：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Can you <strong>change</strong> a £20 note <strong>for</strong> me? 
你能帮我把这20英镑换成零钱吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>change</strong> dollars <strong>into</strong> yen
把美元兑换成日元</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>换乘；转乘 (车、船、飞机等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>All change</strong>! 
全部下车！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>change at</strong> Paris for London
在巴黎中转去伦敦</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I stopped in Moscow only to <strong>change planes</strong>.
我在莫斯科停留只是为了转机。</p></div>

<h4 id="6-ame-exchange">6.★ <strong>退换；调换(AmE exchange)：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>change sth for sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Madam, I want to change this shirt for a larger size.
女士，我想把这件衬衣换成大一号的。</p></div></div>